txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Jagged beaks from the hendrevail found throughout the northern North Downs. Deliver the items to Birgir Listmaster at Othrikar.
'I will mark the task as complete in my lists. We are grateful.'
'You have accepted the request to collect jagged beaks from the hendrevail. You will find them throughout the northern North Downs.'
Birgir Listmaker, one of the miners at Othrikar in the northern reaches of the North Downs, awaits the delivery of jagged beaks.
Deliver the jagged beaks to Birgir Listmaker at Othrikar
